<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉frạḥ ạldnyạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉frạḥ ạldnyạ dy lqlby mạ tsạwy dqạyq mʿdwdẗ
 ạ̉qḍyhạ fy kẖlwẗ mʿ rby bmḥbẗ gẖyr mḥdwdẗ)2
 ạlqrạr- sạʿthạ ysẖạwr wạ̉nạ ạ̉qwl ḥạḍr wạlgẖạly yrkẖṣ wyhwn
 bjhạd ṣạbr ʿn ṭyb kẖạṭr rạḥ ạ̉ṭyʿ ạ̉mrh mhmạ ykwn
 2- (ạḥky lh ysmʿ lṣlạty wbḥb yjạwb ṭlbạty
 wlṣwth hạsmʿ fy ktạbh wbsẖkẖṣh tsʿd ạ̉wqạty)2
 3- (wbrby ạfrḥ wạ̉tldẖdẖ wbḥbh yfhmny klạmh
 wlṣwth hạsmʿ wạnfdẖ wạʿysẖ bạmạnẗ qdạmh)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>3432</hymn_number>
<author>ṣfạʾ ṣbḥy̱, nḥmyạ wdyʿ</author>
</song>